<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Fancy Frage-Webseite</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg1:#0f172a;
      --bg2:#1e293b;
      --accent:#7c3aed;
      --accent2:#22c55e;
      --wrong:#ef4444;
      --text:#e5e7eb;
      --glass:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}

    body{
      min-height:100vh;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(124,58,237,0.45), transparent 35%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(34,197,94,0.25), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg1), var(--bg2));
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .bg-shape{
      position:absolute;
      width:260px;
      height:260px;
      border-radius:50%;
      filter:blur(20px);
      opacity:.35;
      animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .shape1{background:var(--accent); top:8%; left:8%;}
    .shape2{background:var(--accent2); bottom:10%; right:8%; animation-delay:2s;}

    @keyframes float{
      0%,100%{transform:translateY(0px) translateX(0px);}
      50%{transform:translateY(-18px) translateX(12px);}
    }

    .card{
      position:relative;
      width:min(92vw, 540px);
      padding:28px;
      border-radius:24px;
      background:var(--glass);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow:0 18px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    }

    .badge{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:6px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(124,58,237,0.18);
      border:1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.35);
      font-size:.85rem;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    h1{
      font-size:2rem;
      line-height:1.1;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    p{
      color:#cbd5e1;
      line-height:1.6;
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .question-box{
      padding:16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(15,23,42,0.45);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }

    .question-title{
      font-size:1rem;
      color:#f8fafc;
      margin-bottom:10px;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    ul{
      list-style:none;
      display:grid;
      gap:10px;
    }

    li{
      padding:12px 14px;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .form-row{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:14px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    input{
      flex:1;
      min-width:220px;
      padding:14px 16px;
      border:none;
      outline:none;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      color:#111827;
      font-size:1rem;
    }

    button{
      padding:14px 18px;
      border:none;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #2563eb);
      color:white;
      font-weight:700;
      cursor:pointer;
      transition:transform .15s ease, opacity .15s ease;
    }

    button:hover{
      transform:translateY(-1px);
      opacity:.95;
    }

    .result{
      margin-top:16px;
      padding:14px 16px;
      border-radius:14px;
      font-weight:700;
      display:none;
    }

    .correct{background:rgba(34,197,94,0.18); border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.35);}
    .wrong{background:rgba(239,68,68,0.18); border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.35);}

    .hint{
      margin-top:10px;
      font-size:.9rem;
      color:#94a3b8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-shape shape1"></div>
  <div class="bg-shape shape2"></div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="badge">Schul-Quiz • Fancy Edition</div>
    <h1>Suche im Bereich eine Fußballmannschaft</h1>
    <p>Schreibe das heutige Datum in die Antwortzeile. Wenn es falsch ist, erscheint eine falsche Antwort.</p>

    <div class="question-box">
      <div class="question-title">Wähle die richtige Aussage:</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Das richtige Datum ist heute.</li>
        <li>Falsch wäre zum Beispiel: „Geh jetzt in die Mensa“.</li>
        <li>Falsch wäre auch: „Ab auf den Pausenhof“.</li>
        <li>Noch falsch: „Dann direkt in die Aula“.</li>
        <li>Auch falsch: „Jetzt zum Sportplatz“.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="form-row">
      <input id="answer" type="text" placeholder="TT.MM.JJJJ" />
      <button onclick="checkAnswer()">Prüfen</button>
    </div>

    <div id="result" class="result"></div>
    <div class="hint">Beispiel: 09.04.2026</div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function checkAnswer() {
      const input = document.getElementById("answer").value.trim();
      const result = document.getElementById("result");

      const today = new Date();
      const day = String(today.getDate()).padStart(2, "0");
      const month = String(today.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, "0");
      const year = today.getFullYear();
      const correctDate = `${day}.${month}.${year}`;

      result.style.display = "block";

      if (input === correctDate) {
        result.className = "result correct";
        result.textContent = "Richtig! Du hast das Datum korrekt eingegeben.";
      } else {
        result.className = "result wrong";
        result.textContent = "Falsch! Dann ist die Antwort: Geh in die Mensa, in die Aula, auf den Pausenhof oder zum Sportplatz.";
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
